    <h2>Check-in and WiFi</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Address:</strong> Frants Beyers veg 24, 5232 Paradis</li>
      <li><strong>Check-in:</strong> After 4:00 PM or by individual agreement</li>
      <li><strong>Key:</strong> Keyless entry system on the doors. Use the code you received via the platform you booked on (Airbnb/Booking).</li>
      <li><strong>WiFi:</strong> Name: AOGI2 Password: 39153915</li>
      <li><strong>Parking:</strong> There is a large parking area in front of the entrance. You might see one or two of my cars parked there already, but there is plenty of space for several vehicles :-)</li>
